ISLAMABAD, Mar 11 (APP): Justice Supreme Court Munib Akhtar Saturday represented Pakistan virtually at the Shanghai Cooperation Organization (SCO) Chairmen of Supreme Courts meeting held in New Delhi.
Speaking on the subject of “Facilitating Access to Justice”, he expressed support for the rule of law and for promoting the accessibility of legal systems in the SCO member states.
